'''David''' is one of the boys who dared [[Andrew Langston]] to jump in cement.

==History==
[[Kip]], David, and [[Will (Freedom)|Will]] dared [[Andrew Langston]] to lie down in wet cement on a job site. He did it because [[Lola (Freedom)|Lola]] was watching and he wanted to impress her. They then came to the hospital with him, though they continued to make fun of him. ''("[[Freedom, Part 1]]")''

They stayed at the hospital and because of their influence, Lola refused to go see Andrew before his surgery. ''("[[Freedom, Part 2]]")''

==Relationships==
===Friendships===
Kip, David, and Will are friends.
